_sText:
This is a jail map focused on balanced teams.  Rebelling isn't OP and the CT's still have to focus on the t's to make sure they aren't rebelling.

This Jail map includes:
Disco
Pool
Big Cage
DeathRun
Armory Gun Spawners
Lr room
Teleports
Secret Rooms
Vents
Soccer
Basketball
Climb

Check it out, the map is great!

Allows up to 32 players, 1:2 ratio for teams.  Will have heavy support for updates so enjoy the map.
